            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "There‚Äôs always been a problem with stress in newsrooms. The pandemic thrust us all into an apocalyptic situation, and use of user-generated content in our work has brought the sorts of trauma only experience by war reporters in the past into our newsrooms. It‚Äôs time to fix this ‚Äî and a panel at news:rewired discussed how to build resilience in our journalists.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
